      <p>I will assist you in choosing the best tools for the job, whether that is Perplexity, OpenClaw, Claude Code, ChatGPT or Gemini — covering everything from smarter prompting, integrating with Google or custom AI-assisted workflows that save you hours each week. Whether you're running a business, managing projects, or working in a creative field, I'll show you tools and techniques you can use immediately.</p>
